  - Apache Kafka
  - Apache Flink
  - AWS Kinesis
  - Spark Structured Streaming
  - Kafka Streams
  - PostgreSQL
  - BigQuery
  - Snowflake
  - Docker
  - Schema Registry

# === EXAMPLES ===
